sources.title: Navy Seals: The Battle For New Orleans | Full Movie | Action Survival Hindi
sources.description:
In this action-packed thriller starring real Navy Seals, a terrible virus breaks out in New Orleans - turning anyone it infects into ravenous, uncontrollable, superhumans. When violence threatens the Vice President's campaign visit to the area, the CIA sends in Navy Seal Team 6 to secure the Vice President and rescue scientists from a facility whose research could provide the cure.The mission goes quickly awry, however, and a rookie Seal finds himself working with a courageous news reporter to save the Vice President and, ultimately, the world.
2015.  Stars: Ed Quinn, Michael Dudikoff, Rick Fox
